# Vistas Razor (RepoKN)

## Layouts

- Páginas autenticadas: `~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml`
- Login/registro: `~/Views/Shared/_LayoutExterno.cshtml`

## Formularios

```cshtml
@model KN_WEB.Models.UsuarioModel

@using (Html.BeginForm("Registro", "Home", FormMethod.Post, new { @id = "RegistroForm" }))
{
    if (ViewBag.Mensaje != null)
    {
        <div class="alert text-danger" role="alert">@ViewBag.Mensaje</div>
    }
    <div class="form-group position-relative has-icon-left">
        @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.CorreoElectronico, new { @class = "form-control form-control-xl", @placeholder = "Correo Electrónico" })
        <div class="form-control-icon"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg shadow-lg mt-3">Procesar</button>
}
```

## Convenciones

- `Html.BeginForm` + `Html.TextBoxFor` para campos del modelo
- Navegación con `@Url.Action("Action", "Controller")`
- Auth: fila Bootstrap `col-lg-6` / `col-lg-5`, `#auth-left` + `#auth-right`
- Internas: `.page-title` > `.section` > `.card`
- Botón submit: **Procesar**
